  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Influence of Cetuximab on metabolic activation of Capecitabine</measure>
    <time_frame>9 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>Curve fitting of drug and metabolite concentrations will be performed. For pharmacokinetic modelling of CCB and metabolites, a non-compartment model for extravascular input will be used. For calculation of AUC and AUMC the linear trapezoid rule will be applied for the ascending part of the concentraion-time curve and the log-linear trapezoidal rule for the descending part of the concentration-time curve.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
